barbeque sets.

238
00:18:31,639 --> 00:18:35,680
'Selling life and...still waiting.'

239
00:18:35,680 --> 00:18:37,839
Jason!

240
00:18:37,839 --> 00:18:41,719
Kevin! The guy
with the personal hygiene problem.

241
00:18:41,719 --> 00:18:43,880
Nothing changes, really.

242
00:18:43,880 --> 00:18:46,240
Hi, Morag.

243
00:18:46,240 --> 00:18:48,039
Me and Morag used to go out.

244
00:18:48,039 --> 00:18:52,639
So, how come I can remember the
details of my fascinating daily life,

245
00:18:52,639 --> 00:18:55,680
but the vital couple of weeks
before I died

246
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:59,119
are still a complete mystery to me?
Are you Gary?

247
00:18:59,119 --> 00:19:01,640
Yeah, yeah. How do you, er...?

248
00:19:01,640 --> 00:19:06,799
Are you... Gwen, yes.
I was just wondering whether
you saw Eugene the day he died.

249
00:19:06,799 --> 00:19:08,920
No. Sorry.

250
00:19:08,920 --> 00:19:10,799
Just doing a card. You know...

251
00:19:12,559 --> 00:19:17,080
"Good luck in your new job"?!
He's dead. No! Who's it for, then?

252
00:19:17,080 --> 00:19:19,680
His mum, you idiot! Shit.

253
00:19:19,680 --> 00:19:22,519
Can you rub it out? It's in Biro.

254
00:19:22,519 --> 00:19:27,000
People just don't understand.
Don't worry, mate, it's OK.

255
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:29,119
Is it true?

256
00:19:29,119 --> 00:19:32,119
He got run over? Yeah.

257
00:19:32,119 --> 00:19:34,159
Oh, God.

258
00:19:34,159 --> 00:19:38,119
Sorry. I'm Linda.
I'm a Silver Seller.

259
00:19:39,360 --> 00:19:41,960
It's all about belief, see?

260
00:19:41,960 --> 00:19:45,920
If necessary,
I am Kitchens For A Lifetime.

261
00:19:45,920 --> 00:19:48,879
Eugene was only ever himself.

262
00:19:48,879 --> 00:19:50,919
He wasn't the best salesman then?

263
00:19:50,919 --> 00:19:55,880
No. I think Craig kept him on
out of the goodness of his heart.

264
00:19:55,880 --> 00:19:58,840
