409
00:30:12,360 --> 00:30:14,919
So he chose eBay? Cyberspace.

410
00:30:14,919 --> 00:30:18,520
I mean, even an online auction
has a certain elegant symmetry.

411
00:30:20,119 --> 00:30:22,840
I think I'm finally
going to meet him.

412
00:30:22,840 --> 00:30:28,359
Well, I was
doubtful at first, you know, and
then suddenly, out of nowhere - bam!

413
00:30:28,359 --> 00:30:33,000
15,000. I mean, the bid jumped
to a cool cowin' 15,000.

414
00:30:33,000 --> 00:30:35,240
Yeah. Yeah. I remember us talking.

415
00:30:35,240 --> 00:30:38,439
I thought it was £15,005.50.

416
00:30:38,439 --> 00:30:40,320
Yeah, it was, yeah.

417
00:30:40,320 --> 00:30:43,400
I mean, I wouldn't spend that
kind of money unless it was my own

418
00:30:43,400 --> 00:30:47,279
