or something. Would you? No.

419
00:30:47,279 --> 00:30:50,919
No. No way! I remember, yes.

420
00:30:50,919 --> 00:30:56,920
I waited a couple of days and then I
got an email telling me to come to,
er...come to a restaurant.

421
00:30:56,920 --> 00:30:59,559
You saw Eugene the day he died,
didn't you?

422
00:30:59,559 --> 00:31:03,160
Yeah, I met up with him before
