423
00:31:03,160 --> 00:31:04,719
I had a cup of coffee.

424
00:31:04,719 --> 00:31:06,880
He was scared. Was I? Course I was.

425
00:31:06,880 --> 00:31:10,920
So he went to make the exchange -
£15005.50 for the eye, right?

426
00:31:10,920 --> 00:31:14,839
And this was somewhere on the
A48 perhaps? Or not. Or not?

427
00:31:14,839 --> 00:31:16,800
Eugene was very secretive.

428
00:31:16,800 --> 00:31:18,840
Could have been in Splott? Splott?

429
00:31:18,840 --> 00:31:21,559
That doesn't sound right, mate.

430
00:31:21,559 --> 00:31:23,119
Who are these people with you, Gary?

431
00:31:25,920 --> 00:31:28,680
Why would Eugene take
a photo of your shoes?

432
00:31:28,680 --> 00:31:30,959
And, whose are the other shoes?

433
00:31:30,959 --> 00:31:33,039
They're just random shoes,
I should think.

434
00:31:35,400 --> 00:31:37,320
I miss him.

435
00:31:54,880 --> 00:32:00,919
Yes, yes, I can remember!
I called a taxi, and then, then I
put the eye in a freezer bag.

436
00:32:00,919 --> 00:32:06,240
And then there was...
Yes, I was walking up this
road going up towards...

437
00:32:06,240 --> 00:32:09,879
um, a shiny building with...

438
00:32:09,879 --> 00:32:12,840
a great door which
said something about...

439
00:32:12,840 --> 00:32:14,319
something about...

