00:33:27,439 --> 00:33:29,560
I thought we were on holiday.

447
00:33:40,999 --> 00:33:42,799
Yes.

448
00:33:42,799 --> 00:33:44,440
Yes...this is it.

449
00:33:44,440 --> 00:33:49,159
We came up the hill, and there
it was! There it was, the...

450
00:33:52,680 --> 00:33:54,360
The Happy Cook?

451
00:34:10,999 --> 00:34:14,680
Yeah, I walked towards the door,
wondering who exactly I would be

452
00:34:14,680 --> 00:34:20,399
